    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>
        This Chrome extension, Bitcointalk BBCode Extension, is designed to provide enhanced functionality for text formatting within online forums. We take user privacy seriously, and we want to assure you that this extension does not collect, store, or transmit any user data.
    </p>

    <h2>Data Collection:</h2>
    <p>
        Bitcointalk BBCode Extension does not collect any user information, including personal data or browsing history.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services:</h2>
    <p>
        This extension may interact with third-party services or APIs as part of its functionality. However, please note that these interactions do not involve the collection or transmission of user data.
    </p>

    <h2>User Rights:</h2>
    <p>
        Since no user data is collected, there are no data rights or access requests necessary.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact Us:</h2>
    <p>
        If you have any questions or concerns about your privacy while using Bitcointalk BBCode Extension, or if you'd like more information about our privacy practices, please feel free to contact us https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?action=profile;u=1634314.
    </p>

    <p>
        This privacy policy is intended to provide transparency and assurance to users that their privacy is respected while using Bitcointalk BBCode Extension. If you need to provide a contact email or other contact information, make sure it is accurate and actively monitored in case users have questions or concerns.
    </p>
